correct syntax to include header and footer
- the one shown in the video is not working
- correct one is

<%- include('partials/header'); -%>
<%- include('partials/footer'); -%>

to adjust images inside the grid use <img style="width:100%">
    this will put the image using 100% space of the column

if you name your file as index.js than it will automatically require the index file in the code